      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this absolute beauty! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I\u2019ve taken such incredible care of this ride that it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s in truly pristine condition\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found, and it drives like a total dream! It's been my pride and joy, and now it's ready for a new home where it'll be just as loved. If you're looking for perfection on wheels, this is definitely the one for you! Drop me a message, I'd love to chat more about it!",
