    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically peerless 2004 BMW M3 (E46). This example features the legendary S54B32 power plant, characterized by its 8,000-RPM redline and razor-sharp throttle response via six individual throttle bodies. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox shifts with bolt-action precision, paired with a fully serviced variable M differential lock. To ensure structural longevity, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the double-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled. The suspension maintains factory-spec damping rates, providing exceptional lateral grip and communicative feedback. A true enthusiast-grade machine with zero deferred maintenance and pristine compression across all cylinders.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
